* {{FuncArg|number|PrimaryAmmo|Amount of primary ammo in the reserves}}
* {{FuncArg|number|SecondaryAmmo|Amount of secondary ammo. It is shown like alt-fire for SMG1 and AR2 are shown.}}

There is '''no''' SecondaryClip!

